[src:webrtc/api-webrtc-api] An `RTCPeerConnectionIceErrorEvent` indicating that an error has occurred while gathering ICE candidates.
[src:webrtc/api-webrtc-api] Sent to an `RTCPeerConnection` when its ICE connection's state—found in the `iceConnectionState` property—changes.
[src:webrtc/api-webrtc-api] Sent to an `RTCPeerConnection` when its ICE gathering state—found in the `iceGatheringState` property—changes.
